20 hear comments from the public regarding the proposed tax rate. The hearing
21 shall be held in the principal office of the taxing district or, in the event the
22 taxing district has no office, or the office is not suitable for such a hearing, the
23 hearing shall be held in a suitable facility as near as possible to the geographic
24 center of the district.
